news.title: Chandigarh: 18 commercial properties to be auctioned after Diwali
news.para: The estate branch of the municipal corporation (MC) will auction its 18 commercial properties costing Rs 61.71 crore in Manimajra after Diwali.

news.title: Manesar civic body fines two building sites for GRAP violations
news.para: He also said that one site was imposed a penalty of Rs 5 lakh as it was more than 20,000 square metre in area whereas the second site was imposed a fine of Rs 5 lakh as it has an area of 500 square metre.

news.title: PM to hand over keys to 1,144 houses built under central scheme in Rajkot
news.para: The multi-storey residential project having 11 blocks has been built in 20 months using new technology from France for faster construction of houses.
